the identifiers in \CEE/ texts enclosed in \pb, or for control texts
enclosed in \.{@@\^}$\,\ldots\,$\.{@@>} or \.{@@.}$\,\ldots\,$\.{@@>}
or \.{@@:}$\,\ldots\,$\.{@@>}.

